🎙️ Text-to-Speech Converter
A professional, responsive, and easy-to-use Text-to-Speech (TTS) web application built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This tool allows users to input custom text and convert it into natural-sounding speech using the Web Speech API.

🚀 Features
🎧 Converts written text into spoken voice using built-in browser capabilities

🌐 Supports multiple languages and voices (depending on browser support)

🖥️ Responsive and accessible user interface

🎛️ Adjustable pitch, rate, and volume settings (optional)

📱 Fully compatible with modern browsers and mobile devices

🛠️ Technologies Used
HTML5 — Semantic structure

CSS3 — Styling and layout

JavaScript (Vanilla) — Web Speech API integration

📦 How to Use
Clone or Download the repository

Open index.html in any modern browser

Type or paste your text into the input box

Select your preferred voice (if available)

Click "Speak" to hear the spoken output

🔒 Browser Compatibility
✅ Google Chrome

✅ Microsoft Edge

✅ Safari (limited voice support)

⚠️ Firefox (partial support)

